" Ctrl-E to switch between 2 last buffers
nmap <C-E> :b#<CR>

" ,e to fast finding files. just type beginning of a name and hit TAB
nmap <leader>e :e **/

" easy split navigation
nnoremap <C-h> <C-w>h
nnoremap <C-j> <C-w>j
nnoremap <C-k> <C-w>k
nnoremap <C-l> <C-w>l

" open file under cursor in new vertical split
nmap <F13> :vertical wincmd f<CR>